ENONewPartHdr.Title: New Part
ENONewPartHdr.LongHelp: In the dialog box, enter a title, the required attributes if any, and optionally select a template to choose the CAD master. Click <uicontrol>Create and Close</uicontrol> to create only one part, or <uicontrol>Create</uicontrol> to create another one.
ENOInsertNewPartHdr.Title: Insert New Part
ENOInsertNewPartHdr.ShortHelp: Creates a new part and adds it as a child to the selected objects.
ENOInsertNewPartHdr.LongHelp: In the dialog box, enter a title, and optionally select a template to choose the CAD master. Click Create and Close to create only one part, or Create to create another one.
